title: Metallica - Master Tracks - Extracts from Fuel vocal track
description:
Your probably wondering what on earth these files are - these are 4 very short audio files taken from the vocal track for the song Fuel, so its only James singing.

Taken out of context like this they sound quite funny, especially number 3. 

I actually use them as ringtones on my mobile phone!




1st - 'Give me fuel, give me fire, give me that which I desire - oooh' from the intro. 

2nd - james says 'yeah'

3rd - 'So give me fuel, give me fire, give me that which I desire' - ooooh, yeah-eah'. from the second chorus if i remember rightly.

4th - 'Give me fuel, give me fire, give me that which I desire - oooh!' From the very end of the song and sung a bit more intensely.
